  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/75c73f24dd99289c91b005f859e4f587.poster.avif?t=1754448351\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/75c73f24dd99289c91b005f859e4f587.webm?t=1754448351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Castillo: The Nine Circles</strong> is a retro FPS Collectathon mixing the exploration from 90’s platformers with all the carnage you love from the best 90’s shooters. Collect power shards hidden in each circle of hell to unlock new areas in the hub and open 9 diverse worlds.<br><br>Your killer has traveled back in time to torture your past self, even if he must rip apart time to keep you there. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/9432f48a873857a31d97b3bf39c31478.poster.avif?t=1754448351\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/9432f48a873857a31d97b3bf39c31478.webm?t=1754448351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock unique abilities to make it easier to traverse each world.<br></li><li>Destroy a wide cast of monsters with an arsenal of deadly weapons.<br></li><li>Build up large combos for a speed boost.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/1e9e5f8756e33c68bd58312b8be0a76b.poster.avif?t=1754448351\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/1e9e5f8756e33c68bd58312b8be0a76b.webm?t=1754448351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immerse yourself in the 9 circles of hell, each inspired by Dante’s Inferno and teeming with secrets.<br></li><li>Meet an unforgettable cast of characters along with a horde of shiny collectables.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/75c73f24dd99289c91b005f859e4f587.poster.avif?t=1754448351\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/75c73f24dd99289c91b005f859e4f587.webm?t=1754448351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Castillo: The Nine Circles</strong> is a retro FPS Collectathon mixing the exploration from 90’s platformers with all the carnage you love from the best 90’s shooters. Collect power shards hidden in each circle of hell to unlock new areas in the hub and open 9 diverse worlds.<br><br>Your killer has traveled back in time to torture your past self, even if he must rip apart time to keep you there. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/9432f48a873857a31d97b3bf39c31478.poster.avif?t=1754448351\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/9432f48a873857a31d97b3bf39c31478.webm?t=1754448351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock unique abilities to make it easier to traverse each world.<br></li><li>Destroy a wide cast of monsters with an arsenal of deadly weapons.<br></li><li>Build up large combos for a speed boost.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/1e9e5f8756e33c68bd58312b8be0a76b.poster.avif?t=1754448351\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/ap